---
title: California-Inspired Fish Tacos with Guacamole and Lime Crema
description: Taco night just got tastier! Flaky barramundi is coated in enchilada spices and pan-seared for a spicy, charred filling. Top with a pile of zesty coleslaw, savoury guacamole and diced tomatoes for the perfect handheld!
